&lt;html&gt;&lt;div style=&#39;background-color:&#39;&gt;&lt;P&gt;Also, remember that the British pronounciation is different from the American dialect. British is closer to &quot;bizi&quot;, whereas American is distinctly &quot;bizI&quot;.&lt;/P&gt;
&lt;P&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;
